# $JAC Bot Performance Dashboard Implementation Context

## Status
Finalized implementation plan, ready for development.

## Objectives
- Integrate a live bot performance dashboard above the Meme Leaderboard.
- Securely fetch data from MSK Technology API (`https://api.msktechnology.com.au/stats`).

## Architecture & Security
- **Approach**: Vite server proxy (Dev) + Vercel Serverless Function (Prod).
- **Authentication**: `x-api-key` header (stored in `.env`, injected server-side).
- **Hosting**: Vercel.

## UI/UX Design
- **Visual Theme**: Gold + dark glassmorphism (consistent with current design).
- **Metrics**: 
  - Total Revenue (includes a SOL/USD display toggle).
  - SOL Price.
  - $JAC Burned (includes a custom "fire glow" effect).
- **Features**:
  - Live data indicator (pulsing dot).
  - Smooth animated number transitions on data refresh.
  - Toast notifications ("Data updated ✓") on successful refresh.
  - Last Burn TX link to Solscan.

## Technical Details
- **Refresh Rate**: 120 seconds (respecting 1-min API rate limits).
- **No Mock Data**: Dashes will show on error.
- **Reference Document**: See `implementation_dashboard.md` in artifacts for the full changeset and logic.
